<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf6151b0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s12149"><num value="12149">§ 12149.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbf6151b1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s12149/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Not later than 1 year after <date date="1990-07-26">July 26, 1990</date>, the Secretary of Transportation shall issue regulations, in an accessible format, necessary for carrying out this subpart (other than <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s12143">section 12143 of this title</ref>).</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbf6151b2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s12149/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Standards</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The regulations issued under this section and <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s12143">section 12143 of this title</ref> shall include standards applicable to facilities and vehicles covered by this part. The standards shall be consistent with the minimum guidelines and requirements issued by the Architectural and Transportation Barriers Compliance Board in accordance with <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s12204">section 12204 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idbf6151b3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/336/tII/s229">Pub. L. 101–336, title II, § 229</ref>, <date date="1990-07-26">July 26, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/345">104 Stat. 345</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbf6151b4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idbf6151b5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idbf6151b6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1990-07-26">July 26, 1990</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/101/336/s231/b">section 231(b) of Pub. L. 101–336</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s12141">section 12141 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
